Saracens No 8 Billy Vunipola , Toulon flanker Steffon Armitage and Clermont full back Nick Abendanon have all been shortlisted for the European Player of the Year award .
Vunsterola starred for Mark McCall 's side following his side 's 33-10 demolition of Munster in round five .
Saracage was named on the shortlist by Leinster captain Jamie Heaslip and No 8 Fritz Lee .